com.interpss.simu.multicase.datatype
Interface BusPQUpdateRec

All Superinterfaces:
EMFPersistable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
BusPQUpdateRecImpl
public interface BusPQUpdateRec
extends EMFPersistable

A representation of the model object 'Bus PQ Update Rec'. Data record to update a PQ bus. It is used in the multi-net Loadflow algorithm to update the main network from the subnets.

The following features are supported:

  • Lf Converged
  • Bus Id
  • P
  • Q
